# YouTube RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)

A full-stack project that allows users to ask questions about YouTube videos using transcript-based semantic search and LLM-powered responses.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Ask natural language questions about YouTube videos
- Transcript-based semantic retrieval
- FastAPI backend with vector embeddings
- Clean HTML/CSS/JS frontend
- Browser extension support
- Handles transcript errors and rate limits

